{"word":"G521 - ἀπαίδευτος - apaídeutos - ap-ah'-ee-dyoo-tos - Unlearned","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀπαίδευτος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">apaídeutos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ap-ah'-ee-dyoo-tos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Unlearned</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"அயுக்தமுமான - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"without instruction and discipline, une ducated, ignorant, rude"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1 - Α - A - al'-fah/1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and a derivative of <a href=\"#/G3811 - παιδεύω - paideúō - pahee-dyoo'-o/3811\">G3811</a>; <i>uninstructed</i>, that is, (figuratively) <i>stupid:</i> - unlearned.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G3807/3807\">G3807</a>, <a href=\"#/G3809/3809\">G3809</a>, <a href=\"#/G3810/3810\">G3810</a>, <a href=\"#/G3811/3811\">G3811</a>, <a href=\"#/G521/521\">G521</a>"}]}